General.Name: Vanguard International Dividend Appreciation Index Fund ETF Shares
General.Description: The index focuses on common stocks of high-quality companies located in developed and emerging markets, excluding the U.S., that have both the ability and the commitment to grow their dividends over time. The manager attempts to replicate the target index by investing all, or substantially all, of its assets in the collection of securities that make up the index. The fund is non-diversified.
